<lb ed="C I" n="0007a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 3</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>元景造石窟記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a01"/><p id="pI01p0007a0101">惟大魏太和廿三年歲次己卯四<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">月</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">丙</unclear>午朔八日<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">癸</unclear>丑
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a02"/>諸軍事平東將軍營州刺史元景。上為
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a03"/>皇帝陛下敬造石窟一區
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a04"/>夫靈覺沖虛。非像無以<note n="0007001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30346;＝筌【史】</note><app n="0007001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">筌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30346;</rdg></app>其形。妙門潛寂。非唱．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a05"/>生滅。昧識於慧旦。將以輪迴塵網。纏服衰弊<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">矣</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a06"/>釋加如來。契慈心於因初。達妙致於遐劫。．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a07"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">揖</unclear>慧舟以拯溺。夷<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">阻</unclear>濟艱。人天仰德。功蓋．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a08"/>我皇代受命光□□□日新。景福增崇。聖．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a09"/>皇帝陛下。誕<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">稟</unclear>□□□高振古。遊神虛宗。．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a10"/>興援及州鎮。靡不□□況景藉蔭洪□根□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a11"/>土雖麗。豈同巖石之固。於州城東北一百．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a12"/>暨浩滄。右帶龍川。臨清流以藻穢。背脩巒．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a13"/>明。可以軌矚。東民信之。威訓穆然。存道久．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a14"/>皇帝陛下。資化無為。一同率土。享祚齊．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a15"/>明元皇帝。栖神常住。降及一切。普沾．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a16"/>是詣。速證大果。又願己身。并諸眷屬。．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a17"/>文靡述。國之<note n="0007002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">烋＝休【史】</note><app n="0007002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">休</lem><rdg wit="【原】">烋</rdg></app>祉。可無稱乎。故於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">石</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a18"/>玄覺體<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">空</unclear>。真□□□公誰究竟。悟茲．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a19"/>空有同照。無<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">微</unclear>□□。調風灑澤。懷．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a20"/>詳陟<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">人</unclear>合。想<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">作</unclear>□□。彫巖鏤<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">飾</unclear>。．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a21"/>建茲<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">華</unclear>窟。投心請慶。仰願聖．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0007a22"/>上願明元。神栖妙宮。受道．．．</p>
